                <a href="https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/virtual-machines/windows/publish-web-app-from-visual-studio" target="_blank" rel="noopener" tabindex="190">Publish an ASP.NET Web App to an Azure VM from Visual Studio</a>
            </p>
            <p>
                <a href="https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/virtual-machines/windows/snapshot-copy-managed-disk" target="_blank" rel="noopener" tabindex="190">Create a snapshot</a>
            </p>
